=head1 DESCRIPTION

The configuration for input switching based on the media quality
confidence score (MQCS) as provided from AWS Elemental MediaLive.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 MQCSInputSwitching => Bool

When true, AWS Elemental MediaPackage performs input switching based on
the MQCS. Default is true. This setting is valid only when C<InputType>
is C<CMAF>.



